The defendant Jordan C Stokes was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jordan C Stokes is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Jordan C Stokes was found guilty of Possess w/ Intent-THC(>200-1000g), a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(h)2.
